title: Bachelor Michael once dated Kyly Clarke
text:
Email a friend 
BACHELORETTE frontrunner Michael Turnbull has revealed he once dated Michael Clarke’s wife Kyly. 
While the pair’s romance was short lived, the 34-year-old says he took Clarke out on a date back in 2003. 
“From memory I took her to Bondi for lunch and we watched a movie,” the retired professional soccer player told OK! magazine. 
“For whatever reason it didn’t work out.” Kyly and Michael Clarke. Source: Supplied 
Turnbull said the pair saw each other in Sydney recently and were happy to say hello. 
“Just before the show, I saw her while I was out having coffee. We said G’day and had a bit of a chat,” he said. 
It seems there is a bit of history between Turnbull and Michael Clarke. 
A photo of the pair pictured with Clarke’s former fiancee Lara Bingle has emerged from 2008, showing the trio hanging out in Sydney’s The Ivy. 
Turnbull is the second Bachelor to kiss Sam Frost on the dating show, with the pair locking lips during last night’s episode. Michael Turnbull, Michael Clarke and Lara Bingle in 2008. Source: Facebook
